  <title>Changelog For Release 0.3.X</title>
  <section>
    <title>Release 0.3.0</title>
    <section>
      <title>New Features</title>
      <informaltable>
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="4*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry>Feature 409</entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Enabled project specific <filename>LSRLimits.h</filename>. </para>
                <para>In order to build the LSR the cmake variable
  <parameter>HMI_PROJECT_PATH</parameter> needs to be defined now. It shall
  point to a path where <filename>LSRLimits.h</filename> can be found.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>Feature 398</entry>
              <entry>
                <para><emphasis role="bold">Requirement ID:</emphasis> REQ-013-SW Aging
  time</para>
                <para>Added timer utility class: <classname>lsr::Timer</classname></para>
              </entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>Feature 377</entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Added error reporting for drawing errors. Errors from
  <filename>gil.h</filename> (<function>gilGetError()</function>) are now
  reported to <function>lsrGetError()</function>.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
    </section>
  </section>
</section>
